title: [Western Harbor, Seathrak Way]
description: Cobblestones laid in concentric bands spread across the plaza from the four avenues that meet here and wrap around an enormous sandstone fountain.  Glass-sided lanterns hang from wrought iron posts at each intersection, their glaesine panes sparkling in the ambient light.
